{"tid":2183974,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人喺中大讀緊Master，我全班都係支那學生","createTime":"2020-09-01T09:08:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T11:28:26.000Z","uid":8307,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d6e045ca11d258aac11dab498b6b8e401bd78237","tid":2183974,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:08:51.000Z","msg":"細佬我本身係外國讀完degree翻嚟嘅，依加MPhil啱啱開學冇耐<br />\n本身諗住香港大學一定多香港人啦(本身澳洲嗰邊都多支那人)，點知個教授一開zoom就成班喺度互加we7，我本身以為個profatsa都係支那人黎<br />\n點知原來唔係，係全班學生都來自深圳，當下先知出哂事！！<br />\n好彩依加唔洗去學校上堂，我支語唔係幾好，如果唔係做谷project都唔知點算=.=...<br />\n想知係咪得我係咁，有冇其他讀緊大師既師兄講下情況，咩科就唔講，怕畀班支那仔睇到起我底或者比教授針對...<br />\n同埋依加我仲未交學費，想問下如果走數翻去澳洲讀大師仲有冇得諗...<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QM7rrcA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQM7rrcA.gif&h=c853f0a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8af1a95fab395eda887a639061d084998a13ef0f","tid":2183974,"uid":94167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:09:49.000Z","msg":"黎蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"471f878fc2b6f81dfb36abeb5c1c57fd16cac1e8","tid":2183974,"uid":38904,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:10:35.000Z","msg":"香港啲master, 除咗professional master/research master之外<br />\n都係支那人居多"},{"pid":"5d6bd6c0cae99a81dea7182d17834ee7e90b2457","tid":2183974,"uid":22949,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:12:08.000Z","msg":"中大=中國大學，唔是嗎"},{"pid":"11843181827d8372b2cc9f2281b6afb08d92bbf5","tid":2183974,"uid":297230,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"471f878fc2b6f81dfb36abeb5c1c57fd16cac1e8","tid":2183974,"uid":38904,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:10:35.000Z","msg":"香港啲master, 除咗professional master/research master之外<br />\n都係支那人居多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:12:59.000Z","msg":"Mphil都好多大劣人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\